# Session-scoped work artifacts created by specy-road do-next-available-task.
# These are regenerated each pickup; tracking them adds noise to feature
# branches. Briefs (work/brief-*.md) and implementation summaries
# (work/implementation-summary-*.md) are intentionally NOT ignored — they
# document the work and belong on the feature branch.
work/.on-complete-*.yaml
work/prompt-*.md
work/.milestone-session.yaml
